T1  - Anticorruption, Government Subsidies, and Innovation: Evidence from China
AU  - Fang, Lily
AU  - Lerner, Josh
AU  - Wu, Chaopeng
AU  - Zhang, Qi
Y1  - 2022/12/07
PY  - 2022
