T1  - Empirical Model of Dynamic Merger Enforcement—Choosing Ownership Caps in U.S. Radio
AU  - Jeziorski, Przemysław
Y1  - 2023/04/03
PY  - 2023
DA  - 2023/08/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2022.4599
